5:
Welcome, everyone, to the very first
Adventurers' Hanetsuki Tournament!
8:
Grab those hagoita and show us
what you've got!
12:
I guess hanetsuki really caught on in
Palpebra.
15:
I was surprised when I found out
Ellya was the one who got it so
popular.
20:
I thought it would be the perfect
sport for people here. Adventurers
don't usually get to compete
one-on-one with each other!
22:
It helps adventurers become more
conscious of each other, and since
it's just hanetsuki there's no need to
hold back, either!
26: True... I'd love to face you myself!
30: Me too! See you in the finals, okay?
33:
U-um! Levy? C-congratulations on
making it all the way to the
semifinals!
36:
Thank you. Your name's Hannah,
right? If you win your next match,
you'll be in the semifinals too, so I'll
be rooting for you.
39:
Th-thank you so much! A-actually,
Levy, you're the one who inspired me
to be an adventurer!
42:
Really! I'm glad I was able to play a
part in helping you find your dream.
44:
But since we're in the same
competition together, we're rivals
now, too. Let's have no regrets about
the outcome, all right?
47:
Th-that's not true, Levy! I could never
hope to be able to call myself your
rival!
49:
All I do is struggle, and I could never
hope to match the speed of
somebody as amazing as you!
55: Oh... Looks like I'm up next. See you!
59:
If it wasn't for you two, I'd still be
stuck struggling to achieve anything
as a mid-tier adventurer...
61:
No matter how much hype and
praise we might get, at the end of
the day we're all just adventurers,
right?
68:
That girl just now? You can tell she's
not looking forward. It's like she was
looking for a reason to give up.
72:
And Hannah advances to the
semifinals! Next up, she'll be facing
Levy!
76:
...All right. I'll do what I need to as
someone she looks up to.
79:
After all, I've decided that I want to
be a star who cheers on her fans.
83:
You've got this queeeen!
Just one more point!
85:
...There's... just no way I can beat
Levy—
91:
Could you tell me something,
Hannah? Which version of me is the
one you look up to?
95:
Is the Levy Gracia you know and
love somebody who would give up
here?
98:
N-no, she'd never do that! Y-you
would never—
101:
Then prove it to me. Show me
everything you aspire to be!
104:
I'll prove to you that Levy Gracia is
no mere poser!
115: I won't go down so easily! Take this!
120:
And that's a wrap! Levy advances to
finals!
128: I'm up for a rematch anytime.
132:
They're just playing hanetsuki, right?
I feel like I missed something
important.
137:
Next up, the final match! Levy's
opponent is ready to go!
141:
I'm not gonna make this easy for
you, got it?
146: You'd better not. Let's do this, Ellya!
152:
That was a great match. I'm glad I
got to face you in the finals!
156:
The honor's all mine. I'll be much
stronger next time, though, so you'd
better get ready.
164:
She certainly is. She's grown a lot
since New Year's.
168:
Haha, maybe you're right! But I'm
definitely not gonna stop here—
172:
Oh, Lady Levy! I've been looking for
you. I've got great news!
174:
About that one-on-one interview
you had the other day... That flirty
character you played was perfect,
and we couldn't have gotten a
better reception!
176:
We need to make this a regular
thing! Maybe we can market it as a
secret personality to the fans! They'll
go crazy for it!
179:
W-wait a moment! I think we need
to reconsider our direction with that
one!
185:
No. I'll do it. The fans would love the
flirty me, wouldn't they?
188:
I'll never grow if I run from this
opportunity. Allow me to go above
and beyond everyone's
expectations!
197:
I hope you're ready, Levy. Your
producer's got your back!
202: Thank you, Alk! I won't let you down!
205:
I'll overcome my weaknesses... and
give them all everything I've got!
